title: "wickra-embed"
abstract: >-
  An allocation-free, no_std streaming-indicator engine for bare-metal and HFT
  hardware: fixed-latency, O(1) updates with no heap, cross-compiled to
  Cortex-M targets and byte-for-byte identical to the std wickra-core.
type: software
